channel.description:
Stork-PK Remade Version! StorkClient: [url=http://www.speedyshare.com/files/23882743/StorkClient_Beta.rar]http://www.speedyshare.com/files/23882743/StorkClient_Beta.rar[/url]
Credits goes to Swoosh for the control panel, and other webbased stuffs.
Every new player starts with 20 points, sharks, lobbys & pots in bank!
[b][size=11pt][font=trebuchet ms]Stork-PK is a Point based server with only combat skills added.:[/font][/size][/b]
[i] Note: Point system means you gain points for killing monsters, and with those points you can go to the control panel on the website and change your points into levels, but whenever you feel like it you can edit your stats to whatever you want again. [u]Max stat is 120[/u][/i] [img]http://i36.tinypic.com/bd534.png[/img]
[i]Note: You can also trade your points into cash by speaking to the guide, located in Edgeville[/i] [img]http://i34.tinypic.com/16lie87.png[/img]
[size=11pt][b][font=trebuchet ms] Stork-PK is mostly pking based.:[/font][/b][/size]
[i]Items like super sets can be bought from the general store, located in Edgeville. Sharks + lobsters are also added to your bank. Newbie armour/weapons/arrows and amulets can be bought from Falador and Varrock. Runes for magic can be bought from Lumbridge. The Lady can teleport you around from city to city.[/i] [b][font=trebuchet ms] [size=11pt] Armor shop *Falador*:[/size][/font][/b]
[img]http://img266.imageshack.us/img266/7301/armour.png[/img]
[b][font=trebuchet ms] [size=11pt] Weapon shop *Varrock*:[/size][/font][/b]
[img]http://img183.imageshack.us/img183/1368/wepons.png[/img]
[b][font=trebuchet ms] [size=11pt] Ranging shop *Varrock*:[/size][/font][/b]
[img]http://img135.imageshack.us/img135/9606/arrows.png[/img]
[b][font=trebuchet ms] [size=11pt] Magic shop *Lumbridge*:[/size][/font][/b]
[img]http://img142.imageshack.us/img142/8959/magicshop.png[/img]
[b][font=trebuchet ms][size=11pt]Items.:[/size][/font][/b] [i]Rune Armor ( Helms, Plates, Chains, Skirts, Legs, and Kites ) - Greater Demons and Red Black Dragons. Rune Weapons ( 2 Handers and Battle Axes ) - Greater Demons and Red Black Dragons Dragon Weapons ( Long Sword and Battle Axe - Red Black Dragons Dragon Armor ( Medium Helmet and Square Shield - Black Dragons *rare drop*[/i]
[b][font=trebuchet ms][size=11pt]Magic portals and F2P PKing area![/size][/font] [img]http://i33.tinypic.com/ipt9hw.png[/img][/b]
[b][size=11pt][font=trebuchet ms]Clan war arena.:[/font][/size][/b] [img]http://img172.imageshack.us/img172/6272/cwars.png[/img]
[b][font=trebuchet ms][size=11pt] Ingame commands:[/size][/font][/b]
[size=11pt][font=trebuchet ms][b]Other Features: [/b][/font][/size] - Even though google.com is a pking server you're still able to Duel/Stake with other people to win items. - Max stat is 120 ~ max combat level is 150. - Long term server, so no one gets flats in 1 week! - Amazing and funny updates. - Kill and death + ratio and highscores. - Good economy - Afk Room - F2P PKing Area -Magical pools to diffrent wild areas - No cheating/macro ** < Read our rules before you play ** - Always feel free to make a post if you need help! - Great staff! - Admins: Crooks & Enz0 - Hope to see YOU on [url=http://google.com.doesntexist.com]Stork-PK[/url] soon! and more!
General commands: /stuck - [i]stand still for 3 minutes and you can teleport to Barbarian village[/i] /online - [i]shows you the list of people online at that moment[/i] /buy - [i] example /buy 31 1000 = 1000 fire runes[/i]
Subscribers COOMING SOON: /island - [i]brings you to the island you paid for[/i] /out - [i]gets you out of the island, teleports you to Edgeville[/i] /say - [i]global chat[/i]
Clan: /claninvite *name* - [i]invites the specified person to the clan(if you are a clan moderator or the clan creator)[/i] /clankick *name* - [i]kicks the specified person out of the clan(if you are a clan moderator or the clan creator)[/i] clan creator)[/i] /clanleave - [i]to leave your current clan[/i] /c *text* - [i]clanchat[/i]
[img]http://i34.tinypic.com/2v996vn.png[/img]
If you want the Stork-PK feeling back, come join us!
